title: Westminster Cathedral Carol Concert for Barnardo's
desc: A Carol Concert in aid of Barnardo?s is being staged in Westminster Cathedral on December 10th. This Carol Concert involves many young supporters and 2 adult choirs singing popular Christmas Songs plus  celebrity readers.
